  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd 4 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "4 suspects arrested with large amount of stolen goods in Kaluwanchigudi",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kaluwanchigudi police said they have arrested 5 suspects with a large amount of looted goods in Kaluwanchigudi area.",
        "Kaluwanchigudi Police said that the police have seized the goods and gold jewelery suspected to have been looted from the houses under the Kaluwanchigudi Police Division for a long time, yesterday evening (18) and arrested one main suspect and 4 other people who were believed to be accomplices in the robbery.",
        "During this, the police also seized matras, thods, identity cards of house owners, 6 gas cylinders, DVD player, 6500 cash, etc.",
        "In the name of the Batticaloa District Police Council, under the guidance of the Kaluwanchigudi Divisional Assistant Superintendent of Police, a police team including the Sub-Inspector of the Major Crime Division under the leadership of the Kaluwanchigudi Police Station Deputy Inspector General have seized the suspects and the items believed to be stolen.",
        "The police further said that further investigations have been carried out and the suspects and items will be produced in the court."
      ],
